About Victor

I have already given classes to two people: a child of 8 years in primary easily deconcentrated but with whom I could find a good understanding and therefore a good dynamic work, and a high school student Secondary Lycée Henri IV. The latter received the congratulations of the jury of the class council on several occasions.

English

I have studied at the Collège and Lycée Henri IV (Paris 5) where I learned good techniques and methods of learning, method, writing and rigor. I give courses in all subjects, and I can even advise on post-bac orientation with a personalized opinion. I am a sympathetic, understanding, patient and I know what a high school student in difficulty can expect from private lessons.
